    </section>

    <section class="vntour-section">
        <h2 class="vntour-heading-secondary">5. Updates to This Cookie Policy</h2>
        <p>We may revise this policy periodically. All changes will be reflected on this page with the new “Last Updated” date.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="vntour-section">
